# 11. 想いを見守って

Miku: Wooow☆
Miku: Tsukasa's show was so much fun!
KAITO: Yes, it was. He's always coming up with entertaining shows, but the one he did today was particularly good.
Miku: Yeah! Prince Pegasus was really cool, and so was Officer Rabbit!
Miku: He totally got flung halfway around the world, but it was amazing to see him come flying back when Prince Pegasus was in a pickle!
Miku: I really wanna try doing that☆
KAITO: Then, why don't we try our hand at that show?
Miku: Oh, you mean it?!
KAITO: Yes. Tsukasa had to cover multiple roles all by himself, but...
Bear Plushie: I wanna join!
Bunny Plushie: Me too!
KAITO: We have so many plushies here to help. I believe we should be able to turn his story into a very grand show.
Miku: Oooh! Yeah, let's do it☆
Miku: Alright, let's see... It begins with Prince Pegasus and Officer Rabbit meeting in the park!
KAITO: Okay, then, I'll be standing stage left. Miku, you take stage right...
KAITO: (I guess the us from this SEKAI also love doing shows...)
KAITO: (Hehe. I have to think this is another reflection of Tsukasa's feelings.)
KAITO: (I'm looking forward to seeing how their show turns out.)
Miku: “And so, after saving the planet, the Pegasus Adventurers decided to travel into outer space!”
Bunny Plushie: *Applause* Nice work, everyone!
Kitty Plushie: Wow, that was so much fun!
KAITO: It was a good show. Especially the way you all danced, plushies.
Bunny Plushie: Really? Yay...!
KAITO: Is something wrong, Miku?
Miku: I really wanna do this show with Tsukasa, you know...?
KAITO: Huh?
Miku: Doing this show with all of you guys was super fun, but I think Tsukasa being here would make things just that much better...!
KAITO: Yes, I do agree with you on that...
KAITO: Moreover... I hope we get to start doing shows with him after he discovers his true feelings.
Miku: Then, it's settled☆
Miku: Let's go find him, KAITO!
KAITO: Hehe. They're finally going to meet him.
KAITO: No, wait a second... Tsukasa doesn't actually come over to SEKAI until years from now...
Little Tsukasa: Hmm... What should I make my next show about...?
Miku's Voice: <Tsukasa. Tsukasa!>
Little Tsukasa: Huh? Whose voice was that...?
Miku: <Over here, Tsukasa...!>
Little Tsukasa: Oh! I might be able to use that stick over there for my next show!!
Little Tsukasa: Prince Pegasus will wield it...! I dub thee the Special Sky Legend Pegasus Sword!
Little Tsukasa: Yes, that's got a good ring to it! I can start working on a show based on that!
KAITO: <Oh...>
Miku: <Hmm... Did we come at the wrong time...?>
Miku: <No matter! We'll just have to do better next time to grab his attention☆>
Little Tsukasa: Haha! This show's so good!
Little Tsukasa: Oh, I could use what they just talked about for my show! Let's see...
Miku: <Tsukasa! I wanna do a show with you!>
Little Tsukasa: Huh?
Little Tsukasa: Oh, someone's calling! What if it's about Saki...?!
Miku: <Oh no!>
Little Tsukasa: Hello?! You've reached the Tenmas! Oh, Toya, it's you...!
Little Tsukasa: Actually, you called at the perfect time! I'm working on my next show and was wondering if you...
Miku: <H-Huh...?>
Miku: <No, I have to keep trying!!>
Miku: <Tsukasa, please find “Untitled” on your phone!>
Little Tsukasa: Huh?! Whoa!!!
Little Tsukasa: What was that just now...? Wait, huh?!
Little Tsukasa: N-No, I dropped my phone in that puddle...! I hope it's not broken...
Miku: I don't understand! Why isn't Tsukasa noticing me?!
KAITO: And now, we won't be able to see him until his phone gets repaired...
KAITO: Still, I didn't think you'd be this invisible to him...
KAITO: That being said...
KAITO: I don't think you need to feel so anxious.
Miku: Huh?
KAITO: Tsukasa's doing his best to come up with another show for Saki right now.
KAITO: So, for now, we may want to just watch over him and give his feelings time to develop further.
Miku: Okay...!
KAITO: (They've been watching over Tsukasa and keeping an eye on his feelings ever since he was little...)
KAITO: (Still, not being able to talk to him due to all those near misses must've been frustrating...)
Little Tsukasa: She really enjoyed my last show! So, I'll try coming up with a sequel for it...!
Junior High School Tsukasa: *Sigh* Saki's hospital is so far away now. I'm getting fewer chances to do shows for her...
Junior High School Tsukasa: No, if I have time to mope, then I have time to hone my acting skills...
Junior High School Tsukasa: Plus, Saki has Ichika and the others...
Junior High School Tsukasa: So, I should focus on becoming the world's greatest star!
Tsukasa: Ah, that was an excellent piece of acting I did just now, was it not?!
Tsukasa: Hehehe. The day I become the greatest star in the world is just around the corner! Hah hah hah hah!
Miku: <Wh-What do we do...?! It's like Tsukasa only cares about becoming the world's greatest star now...!>
KAITO: <Do you think this has anything to do with the person he was trying to make smile being sent far away...?>
KAITO: <He's become so enamored with becoming a star that she's ended up having to take a back seat...>
Miku: <We can't let things continue like this...!>
Miku: <Tsukasa! Tsukasa! Please notice “Untitled” on your phone!>
Miku: <Remember your true feelings...!>
Tsukasa: Sally sells seashells by the seashore!
Miku: <No! He still can't hear me!>
Bunny Plushie: *Cry* Tsukasa's forgotten about his true feelings...!
Miku: Does this mean he's never ever going to learn about this SEKAI?
KAITO: ...
KAITO: No, I don't think he's completely forgotten...
KAITO: I mean, he still cares deeply about doing shows...
KAITO: I'm sure he'll be fine as long as that holds true...
Miku: KAITO...
KAITO: So, until he does remember his true feelings, let's keep trying to talk to him.
KAITO: After all, isn't that why we're here?
Miku: You're right...!
Miku: For his sake, I'm gonna keep trying my best!
Bunny Plushie: Me too...!
Bunny Plushie: Is there anything we can do to help him?
Miku: Hmm...
Miku: Oh, he might remember if he met some people who feel the same way as him!
Miku: What if we tried searching for them?
KAITO: (People who feel the same way as him...?)
KAITO: Oh...
KAITO: (Right... He'll meet Emu and the others soon.)
Bunny Plushie: But how do we find them...?
Miku: Hmm... What if we tried popping over to the phones of people who seem to fit that description...?
Miku: Alright, let's try brainstorming with the other plushies!
Bunny Plushie: Okay, let's go find them!
Miku: Go go☆ Let's go, KAITO!
KAITO: Ah, I'll join you all in a minute. Feel free to start without me.
Miku: Okay☆ Then, let's go!
KAITO: ...
KAITO: I'm sure things will work out.
KAITO: This SEKAI came to be because Tsukasa genuinely wishes to make others smile through his shows...
KAITO: He may've forgotten about that temporarily, but I'm sure he'll remember...
KAITO: I mean, he is the one who produced this spectacular SEKAI.
KAITO: Don't worry.
KAITO: He'll remember.
KAITO: And Miku's right. Those who feel the same way as him will also come visit.
KAITO: Emu, Nene and Rui... They're all wonderful people with good and pure intentions.
KAITO: And they'll help him.
KAITO: They'll help Tsukasa rediscover his true feelings and begin their journey as a troupe.
KAITO: If you keep at it and believe in them, things will turn out.
KAITO: ...
KAITO: We need to do our best.
KAITO: To make sure Tsukasa rediscovers his true feelings.
